                    adipisci aliquam, dolorum et dolor accusamus repellat, impedit ducimus! Consectetur, cupiditate
                    voluptatum?
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-xl-6"
                 style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                <img class="img-fluid" src="/Imagenes/450_1000.jpg"
                     style="border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35) 0px 10px 15px;" width="500cm" height="300cm">
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row my-3" data-aos="fade-up">
            <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 col-xl-6 my-3">
